         I am an Erudite Necro...if I remember correctly, everything you will need at your level can be bought at the underground area in Freeport with no problems other than maybe figuring out how to get to the vendors without dying.  Use invis versus undead to avoid the drowned citizens in the underground.  Also, when you get high enough that you need to start buying spells at the Overthere outpost, you should be able to go there as well with no problem.</P><P>Ozznusyen Zuulavv,<BR>56th Defiler<BR>Brell Serilis</P><P> <a href="#top"><img src="icon_go_up.gif" height="15" width="15" border="0" align="right" alt="Go to Top of Page"></a></font></td>
