         A few places you can try are the evil guilds in qeynos, which is fairly close to Paineel. Dont think you'll be kos, and I believe that you can buy your spells and use the banker there too. At least my erudite necro could. Only problem is you may have a hard time finding the guild! <img src=icon_smile_wink.gif border=0 align=middle> Another place is dark elf necro guilds of course, you wont be kos there, except to the ghouls that guard the entrance to the place, but thats simple enough, just cast Insisibility vs. Undead. THe last place you may want to get some spells is either Oggok or Grobb. THe problem is, you'll be very kos in both these places. THe spells will be in the SK guilds of thesse cities. The only thing you can do is find someone who isnt kos, pray that they are trustworthy, hand them them the money and ask them if they can go get the spell for you. Hope this helps. <img src=icon_smile.gif border=0 align=middle></P><P>Arkken Bloodyskull - Da Original One & Only Necromancahhhh of Thule! PH34R M4H!!<a href="#top"><img src="icon_go_up.gif" height="15" width="15" border="0" align="right" alt="Go to Top of Page"></a></font></td>
